Does that change the way you perceive myself and my achievements?
The world doesn't see people like me as champions.
Not so long ago, people like me were running away and hiding.
The Special Olympics have evolved a lot since the beginning in 1968, but too often people with intellectual disabilities are invisible to the general public.
